subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Anabel Medina Garrigues rallied to beat Yanina Wickmayer, 1-6, 6-3, 6-3, in the first round at the Strasbourg International in France. But four seeded players, including No. 5 Tamarine Tanasugarn and No. 6 Elena Vesnina, lost on a day of upsets in the tuneup tournament for the French Open.
